nces.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-The-Black-Keys-performances-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-The-Black-Keys-performances-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-The-Black-Keys-performances-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-The-Black-Keys-performances-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-The-Black-Keys-performances-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher</a> ) 昨晚（5 月 7 日）意外亮相<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-black-keys">The Black Keys</a>在伦敦举行的演出。看看下面的那一刻的镜头。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-32-noel-gallagher-beck-tour-tickets-indie-sleaze-strokes-glastonbury-3431217">黑键乐队谈论重返英国和他们的“史诗”新专辑</a></strong></li></ul><p>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dan-auerbach">丹·奥尔巴赫 (Dan Auerbach)</a>和帕特里克·卡尼 (Patrick Carney) 组成的美国二人组目前正在进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-add-third-london-brixton-academy-show-to-spring-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-3609204">“国际球员巡演”的英国和爱尔兰站</a>，在那里他们将展示他们的最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-black-keys-ohio-players-review-3612585">“俄亥俄球员”</a> 。</p><p>加拉格尔被认为是专辑中歌曲“You&#39;ll Pay”、“Only Love Matters”和“On The Game”的共同创作者，他还为歌曲剪辑贡献了和声和电吉他。</p><p>在 O2 Academy Brixton 举办的三场 Black Keys 演出中的第一场中，乐队邀请了这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>音乐家与他们一起进行安可表演——从后两首歌开始。</p><p>在这里观看客串的粉丝镜头： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Black Keys - Only Love Matters (与 Noel Gallagher 合作) 在伦敦 (O2 Academy Brixton, 07/05/2024)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/42vBIDQg_hk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Black Keys - On The Game（与 Noel Gallagher 合作）伦敦现场演出（O2 Academy Brixton，2024 年 7 月 5 日）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kXyd386V5Cs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2><strong>黑键乐队的歌单是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>&#39;我拿到我的了&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;梁上黄金&#39;<br /> “你的触摸”<br /> &#39;勒紧，加强&#39;<br /> “有爱，就会旅行”<br /> 《永恒之光》<br /> 《下一个女孩》<br /> &#39;低-高&#39;<br /> “这里无处可去”<br /> 《沉重的灵魂》<br /> 《爱的重量》<br /> &#39;豪林为你&#39;<br /> “美丽的人（保持兴奋）”<br /> &#39;发烧&#39;<br /> &#39;野孩子&#39;<br /> “我通过小道消息听说”（Gladys Knight 和 the Pips 封面）<br /> 《她早已离去》<br /> “小黑潜艇”</strong></p><p><strong>安可<br />“只有爱才重要”（与诺尔·加拉格尔合作）<br /> “On The Game”（与诺埃尔·加拉格尔合作）<br /> &#39;孤单的孩子&#39;</strong></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-32-noel-gallagher-beck-tour-tickets-indie-sleaze-strokes-glastonbury-3431217">去年，The Black Keys 在接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>回忆了他们在录音室与“不可思议的”加拉格尔合作的时光。 “他很搞笑，而且非常有才华，”卡尼说。 “我们称他为‘和弦大师’，因为他是一位完美主义者。”</p><p>他继续说道：“丹和我都是他和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆</a>的忠实粉丝。 “事实上，利亚姆的歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/liam-gallagher-dave-grohl-new-song-everythings-electric-3153212">《Everything&#39;s Electric》</a>是我们决定与[制作人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greg-kurstin">格雷格]库斯汀</a>合作的原因。”</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">High Flying Birds</a>主唱后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-says-songs-hes-co-written-with-the-black-keys-are-fucking-amazing-3455959">称他贡献的三首 Black Keys 歌曲“太棒了”</a> 。</p><p>继都柏林和卡迪夫的演出之后，黑键乐队计划于今晚（5 月 8 日）和明晚（9 日）再次在 O2 Academy Brixton 演出。由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/co-op-live-staff-member-couldnt-stop-crying-after-venues-chaotic-failed-opening-3753532">场地持续存在问题，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchesters-co-op-live-arena-sees-further-problems-and-delays-as-the-black-keys-and-peter-kay-forced-to-postpone-shows-3751134">他们最近被迫推迟在曼彻斯特新的 Co-Op Live Arena 的演出</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Noel Gallagher 谈“议会天空”、人工智能绿洲、1975 年和英国脱欧" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>您可以在下方查看 The Black Keys 2024 年英国巡演的剩余日期，并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/the-black-keys-tickets/artist/847164?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkHQ1PxOcSNiXA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处查找所有剩余门票</a>。</p><h2><strong>黑键乐队即将在英国演出的节目有：</strong></h2><p><strong>可能</strong><br /><strong>08 – 伦敦布里克斯顿 O2 学院</strong><br /><strong>09 – 伦敦布里克斯顿 O2 学院</strong><br /><strong>15 - Co-Op Live Arena，曼彻斯特（重新安排日期）</strong></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-announce-north-american-international-players-tour-2024-dates-buy-tickets-3612569">随后，两人将在秋季开始一系列北美演出</a>，您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/the-black-keys-tickets/artist/847164?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=QHQVEUQchxyPR5sWCQS0k2gbUkHQ1K32cSNiXA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到剩余的门票</a>。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-black-keys-ohio-players-review-3612585">《Ohio Players》的三星级评论</a>中， 